Blackfang had been knocked backwards and stood up on his elbow.

Blackfang: We didn't because you were gravely wounded and because one
of your comrades decided that we could do the job to fix you up.
That's why you're here and you're still yourself.

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, "raccoon7679" <logomorph@h...> wrote:
> KitKat::
> 
> Her optics hadn't adjusted to the light when she heard a small 
> child's voice. She blinked and rubbed her optics. Her optics were 
> coming into focus when the little girl said she was a maximal. She 
> jumped out of the Cr chamber,  jumping over Cam's head and lands on 
> all four paws, looking at the child. "Your a maximal?" She looked 
> around and her optics landed on Blackfang. She stared at him for a 
> moment. "If your a maximal, then why are my commands, still intact? 
> TERRORIZE!"  And transforms into bot mode. Her black matte body, 
> sleek and slender. Her wolf tail flowing behind her. Her red optics 
> bright and vibrant. Her stood there,looking at Blackfang, then to 
> Cam, and back to Blackfang. "Why am I here?" Her face showing no 
> fear, but puzzlement. "Why didn't you kill me? Or let me die?"
